contents.title: Gallery-2
contents.description_html:
Copyright © Melissa Santamaría, 2022

This collection of images by Melissa Santamaría explores the intricate interplay between perception and reality, offering a captivating visual experience that challenges the viewer's understanding of space and form. The series delves into the concept of illusion, using subtle distortions and unexpected compositions to evoke a sense of disorientation and wonder.

contents.title: Albert Einstein Quote
contents.content_html: “Reality is merely an illusion, albeit a very persistent one.” ― Albert Einstein
contents.description_html: A reflection on the nature of reality by Albert Einstein. This quote aligns with the theme of illusion, suggesting that what we perceive as real may be more fluid than we think.
